data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 2-story, 3-bedroom, 2 1/2-bath townhome, meticulously remodeled in 2022, offering the perfect blend of modern elegance and comfortable living. Nestled in a charming community east of the river, this end unit is your gateway to the vibrant and newly renovated downtown Algonquin. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and the tasteful upgrades throughout. The heart of this home is the remodeled kitchen, boasting stunning granite countertops, which perfectly complement the all-new stainless steel appliances. The sleek new kitchen faucet adds a touch of sophistication, and a walk-in pantry with a charming barn door provides ample storage space.  The main level features new flooring, ensuring a cohesive and contemporary feel throughout the home. The luxury carpet on the second floor comes with 8-pound padding for added comfort. The entire interior was professionally painted in 2022, using a neutral color palette that allows you to personalize your space effortlessly.  This townhome is truly move-in ready, making it an ideal choice for those seeking convenience and style. The finished basement offers additional living space, perfect for a home office, gym, or recreation area. Which also includes a storage/utility room. Step outside to the large deck, where you can entertain guests or simply unwind in your outdoor oasis.  For added convenience and safety, the exterior lighting has been updated both in the front and back of the property. You'll also find brand-new ceiling fans to keep you comfortable year-round, and all vents have been meticulously sanitized.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautifully remodeled townhome your own. With its prime location, modern amenities, and proximity to downtown Algonquin, you don't want to miss this opportunity. Schedule a showing today and start living the lifestyle you've always dreamed of! 1 year Premier Home Warranty Included.
